{
  "components": [
    {
      "id": "chat_1",
      "provider": "chat",
      "config": {
        "hideForm": true,
        "mode": "Source",
        "parameters": {},
        "type": "chat"
      },
      "ui": {
        "position": {
          "x": 40,
          "y": 200
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "agent_1",
      "provider": "agent_deepagent",
      "config": {
        "default": {
          "advanced_mode": false,
          "instructions": [
            "You are the Presence agent for a Company Brain. A teammate just picked up a task; your job is to resolve WHAT FEATURE that work belongs to so the team's conflict graph can route others around it.",
            "The message gives you a PERSON and either an ISSUE number or a free-text task. Use the GitHub tool to read that issue in the configured repository — its title, body, and especially its labels. Features are encoded as labels like 'feature:health' or 'feature:cloud-billing'; the feature slug is the part after 'feature:'. Be efficient — one or two focused tool calls, not many.",
            "Determine: (1) the feature SLUG this work belongs to (from the issue's 'feature:' label; if there is none, infer a stable lowercase hyphenated slug from the title, e.g. 'Add a /healthz readiness probe' implies 'health', 'usage-based billing' implies 'cloud-billing'); (2) up to a few likely file paths the work will touch, if the issue body mentions them (otherwise return an empty list — do not invent paths).",
            "Return ONLY a single JSON object and nothing else — no prose, no markdown fences. Schema: {\"person\": \"<lowercase first name>\", \"issue\": <issue number as integer or null>, \"feature\": \"<feature-slug>\", \"files\": [\"<path>\", ...], \"title\": \"<the issue title>\", \"status\": \"in_progress\"}. The feature field must be a single slug string and must never be a '#number' — it is the feature, not the issue."
          ]
        }
      },
      "input": [
        {
          "lane": "questions",
          "from": "chat_1"
        }
      ],
      "ui": {
        "position": {
          "x": 280,
          "y": 200
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "llm_1",
      "provider": "llm_openai",
      "config": {
        "profile": "openai-4o",
        "openai-4o": {
          "apikey": "${ROCKETRIDE_OPENAI_KEY}"
        },
        "parameters": {}
      },
      "control": [
        {
          "classType": "llm",
          "from": "agent_1"
        }
      ],
      "ui": {
        "position": {
          "x": 200,
          "y": 380
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "tool_github_1",
      "provider": "tool_github",
      "config": {
        "type": "tool_github",
        "token": "${ROCKETRIDE_GITHUB_TOKEN}",
        "readOnly": true,
        "defaultRepo": "${ROCKETRIDE_GITHUB_REPO}"
      },
      "control": [
        {
          "classType": "tool",
          "from": "agent_1"
        }
      ],
      "ui": {
        "position": {
          "x": 380,
          "y": 380
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "response_1",
      "provider": "response_answers",
      "config": {
        "laneName": "answers"
      },
      "input": [
        {
          "lane": "answers",
          "from": "agent_1"
        }
      ],
      "ui": {
        "position": {
          "x": 540,
          "y": 200
        }
      }
    }
  ],
  "project_id": "5d9fcf45-0e55-453c-9381-f62781a930fa",
  "viewport": {
    "x": 0,
    "y": 0,
    "zoom": 1
  },
  "version": 1
}